=head1 DEPENDENCIES

GNU B<parallel> uses Perl, and the Perl modules Getopt::Long, IPC::Open3,
Symbol, IO::File, POSIX, and File::Temp.


=head1 SEE ALSO

B<find>(1), B<xargs>(1), B<pexec>(1), B<ppss>(1)

